  "description": "Demolition of the existing building (and associated structures) and construction of a replica replacement building, including the construction of a single-storey rear extension at ground floor level; the construction of a two-storey infill extension together with the construction of a rear roof extension; the installation of windows in the side elevation; excavation of a full-depth basement with associated front and rear lightwells and reconstruction works to the front elevation.",
  "title_number": [
    "258148"
  ],
  "site_number": "42",
  "lapsed_date": "26/06/2023",
  "lpa_name": "Hackney",
  "uprn": "100021026157",
  "appeal_status": null,
  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed rear roof extension, by reason of its size, positioning and scale, would result in an overdominant, unsympathetic and uncharacteristic addition which would fail to compliment the host dwellinghouse and the terrace of which it forms part contrary to policy D4 (Delivering good design) of the London Plan (2021), policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020) and the recommendations of the Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Extensions and Alterations 2009.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed demolition and rebuild, by reason of the loss of original fabric and detailed design, would result in a unsympathetic and uncharacteristic form of development which would harm the character and appearance of the site, adjoining terrace and the surrounding wider streetscene of which it forms part contrary to policy D4 (Delivering good design) of the London Plan (2021), policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020) and the recommendations of the Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Extensions and Alterations 2009.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of the demolition works and failure to demonstrate that the replacement building will achieve zero carbon would result in an unsustainable form of development contrary to policy &amp;nbsp;SI 2 (Minimising greenhouse gas emissions) of the London Plan (2021) and policy LP55 (Mitigating Climate Change) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020).&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
  "subdivision_of_building": null,
  "last_updated_by": "Idox Tascomi"
